Bobo Mbuthu's family can finally come to terms with their loss. A DNA test positively identified the remains found in a Tongaat River as Mbuthu. Courtesy of #DStv403 TONGAAT - Nduduzo "Bobo" Mbuthu's family can finally come to terms with their loss. A DNA test positively matched the remains found in a Tongaat river. The 16-year-old was last seen at a local lounge. READ: Outrage over missing Tongaat teen He was allegedly beaten to death after being accused of stealing alcohol. Seven people accused of involvement in his death face kidnapping and murder charges.